<li>
<p>provider-config resolution for GitHub, Atlassian, Jira override, and Con=
fluence override</p></li>
<li>
<p>source-version binding rules in <code>associate</code></p></li>
<li>
<p>target-version binding rules in <code>associate</code></p></li>
<li>
<p>commit association binding during <code>knowledge add --commit</code></p=
></li>
</ul>
