<p><code>knowledge_add.feature</code></p></li>
<li>
<p><code>knowledge_add_commit.feature</code></p></li>
<li>
<p><code>knowledge_associate_commit.feature</code></p></li>
<li>
<p><code>knowledge_associate_knowledge.feature</code></p></li>
