<h2 id=3D"Knowledge-FeatureSpecification-18.RolloutPlan">18. Rollout Plan</=
h2>
<h3 id=3D"Knowledge-FeatureSpecification-Phase1-CurrentMVPimplementedslice"=
>Phase 1 - Current MVP implemented slice</h3>
<p>Ships:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><code>bitloops devql knowledge add</code></p></li>
<li>
<p><code>bitloops devql knowledge associate</code></p></li>
<li>
<p><code>bitloops devql knowledge refresh</code></p></li>
<li>
<p><code>bitloops devql knowledge versions</code></p></li>
<li>
<p>GitHub issue ingestion</p></li>
<li>
<p>GitHub PR ingestion</p></li>
<li>
<p>Jira issue ingestion</p></li>
<li>
<p>Confluence page ingestion</p></li>
<li>
<p>optional <code>--commit</code> association</p></li>
<li>
<p>version-aware knowledge refs</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>knowledge()</code> repository inventory stage</p></li>
<li>
<p>repo-local <code>knowledge.providers</code> config</p></li>
<li>
<p>shared <code>knowledge.providers.atlassian</code></p></li>
<li>
<p>blob + DuckDB + relational storage split</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"Knowledge-FeatureSpecification-Phase2-Broaderretrievalworkflows">=
Phase 2 - Broader retrieval workflows</h3>
<p>Ships later:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>richer traversal and retrieval surface</p></li>
<li>
<p>better <code>knowledge()</code> composition semantics</p></li>
<li>
<p>current-state projections over immutable assertion history where useful<=
/p></li>
<li>
<p>retrieval modes that distinguish exact historical assertions from derive=
d latest/current-state views</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"Knowledge-FeatureSpecification-Phase3-Discussionenrichment">Phase=
 3 - Discussion enrichment</h3>
<p>Ships later:</p>
<ul>
