<li>
<p>improved diagnostics and richer operator ergonomics for advanced flows</=
p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"Knowledge-FeatureSpecification-19.DefinitionOfDone">19. Definitio=
n Of Done</h2>
<h3 id=3D"Knowledge-FeatureSpecification-CurrentMVPimplementedslice">Curren=
t MVP implemented slice</h3>
<p>The current implemented slice is Done when:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>manual URL ingestion works for GitHub pull requests, GitHub issues, Jira=
 issues, and Confluence pages</p></li>
<li>
<p>repository-scoped knowledge works without requiring commit linkage</p></=
li>
<li>
<p>optional <code>--commit</code> creates the expected commit association</=
p></li>
<li>
<p>manual association works for knowledge -&gt; knowledge, knowledge -&gt; =
commit, knowledge -&gt; checkpoint, and knowledge -&gt; artefact</p></li>
<li>
<p>refresh preserves historical relation bindings</p></li>
<li>
<p>version inspection exposes immutable history</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>knowledge()</code> lists repository knowledge inventory</p></li>
<li>
<p>knowledge storage is idempotent and versioned by content hash</p></li>
<li>
<p>full source payloads are preserved in blob storage</p></li>
<li>
<p>normalized/queryable document-version metadata is persisted in DuckDB</p=
></li>
<li>
<p>identities and relation assertions are persisted in the relational store=
</p></li>
<li>
<p>Atlassian shared config and provider-specific overrides are supported</p=
></li>
<li>
<p>tests are written and passing</p></li>
<li>
<p>documentation is updated to match the implemented slice and planned next=
 phases</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"Knowledge-FeatureSpecification-Broaderfeaturefamily">Broader feat=
ure family</h3>
<p>The broader Knowledge feature family is Done when:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>discussion enrichment preserves canonical root content while storing str=
uctured discussion separately</p></li>
<li>
<p>optional child ingestion is supported where intentionally requested</p><=
/li>
<li>
<p>richer retrieval/traversal semantics are exposed cleanly</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>historicalIntent()</code> is implemented as a derived retrieval la=
yer over the same graph</p></li>
</ul>
